Help - mipov.net

Sign up

To create your account, please provide your first and last name as they appear on your social profiles. You'll also need to enter a valid email address, choose a unique username, and create a strong password (between 6 and 255 characters). Your email will be used for login and important notifications, while your username will be your identity on the platform. Let's get started on connecting your social networks and sharing your profile with the world!

Login

Enter the email address and password you used during sign-up. Your email is your unique identifier, and it helps us keep your account secure. If you've forgotten your password, use the 'Forgot Password' link to reset it. Logging in will allow you to connect with your social networks and manage your profile effortlessly. Let's get you signed in so you can continue sharing and discovering!

How to change password?

To change your password, follow these steps:

  1. Log In: Start by logging into the website with your email and current password.

  2. Access Profile: Once logged in, navigate to the top right corner of the page. Click on the menu and find the link labeled "Profile."

  3. Find Password Section: In your profile settings, locate the section dedicated to password management.

  4. Enter Old and New Password: To update your password, enter your current password for verification. Then, choose a new password and enter it in the designated field. Make sure your new password is strong and secure.

  5. Save Changes: After entering the necessary information, save your changes to update your password.

By following these steps, you can ensure your account remains secure with an updated password. If you encounter any issues, please contact our support team for assistance.

How to add my social profile links?

To add links, follow the steps above:

  1. Login or Sign Up:

    First, you need to either log in to your existing account or sign up for a new one.

  2. Access User Section:

    Once you are logged in, navigate to the user section located in the top right corner of the page.

    Click on the Links option in the menu.

  3. Add Your Link:

    On the links page, you will find fields to enter your link details:

    • Link Title: This is the title that users will see.
    • Profile Link: Enter the URL of the link you want to add.

  4. Save Your Link:

    After entering the required details, press the Save button to add your link to your profile.

  5. View as Guest:

    If you want to see how your profile looks to others, click on the View as Guest link located below your profile card.

By following these steps, you can easily add links to your mipov.net profile and manage how they are displayed to others. If you encounter any issues, please reach out to our support team for assistance.
